title: 253: Black Monday Fallout, Bowl Season Recap
itunes:title: 253: Black Monday Fallout, Bowl Season Recap
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks ask which open job is the most attractive to prospective coaches and GMs (00:30). The guys then dive into their recent scouting trips to the major bowl games and break down what they saw from the future NFL stars (7:10).
